## Template Structure
Always use this base structure for new project templates:

```blade
@extends('layouts.app')

@section('title', 'Project Name - Inkblade.cloud')

@push('styles')
<style>
    .project-container {
        padding: 80px 20px 40px;
        min-height: calc(100vh - 70px);
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #002b36 0%, #073642 100%);
        font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', 'Courier New', monospace;
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .project-container { padding: 60px 15px 30px; }
    }
</style>
@endpush

@section('content')
<div class="project-container">
    <!-- Project content -->
</div>
@endsection
```

## Styling Rules
- Use Solarized Dark colors only
- Mobile-first responsive design
- JetBrains Mono font family
- Touch targets minimum 48px
- Use `@push('styles')` for page-specific CSS

## Project Integration
For new projects, follow this pattern:
1. Create `resources/views/projects/{name}/index.blade.php`
2. Add entry to [ProjectSeeder.php](mdc:database/seeders/ProjectSeeder.php)
3. Update [ProjectController.php](mdc:app/Http/Controllers/ProjectController.php) show() method
4. Test responsive design on all breakpoints